*** Settings ***
Documentation    Common setup, variables, and keywords shared across all suites.
Library          SeleniumLibrary
Library          Collections
Library          String

*** Variables ***
${BROWSER}           chrome
${BASE_URL}          {{baseUrl}}
${TIMEOUT}           30s
${USERNAME}          {{testUsername}}
${PASSWORD}          {{testPassword}}

# Locators (SauceDemo defaults — update for your app)
${USERNAME_FIELD}    id:user-name
${PASSWORD_FIELD}    id:password
${LOGIN_BUTTON}      id:login-button
${ERROR_MESSAGE}     css:[data-test='error']

*** Keywords ***
Open Browser To Login Page
    [Documentation]    Open a browser on the configured BASE_URL.
    Open Browser                    ${BASE_URL}    ${BROWSER}
    Maximize Browser Window
    Set Selenium Implicit Wait      ${TIMEOUT}

Close Browser Session
    [Documentation]    Close the Selenium browser.
    Close Browser

Take Screenshot On Failure
    [Documentation]    Capture a screenshot if the just-finished test failed.
    Run Keyword If Test Failed      Capture Page Screenshot

Wait And Input Text
    [Documentation]    Wait for an input to be visible, then type into it.
    [Arguments]    ${locator}    ${text}
    Wait Until Element Is Visible    ${locator}    ${TIMEOUT}
    Input Text                       ${locator}    ${text}

Wait And Click Element
    [Documentation]    Wait for an element to be visible, then click it.
    [Arguments]    ${locator}
    Wait Until Element Is Visible    ${locator}    ${TIMEOUT}
    Click Element                    ${locator}
